{"tid":1897812,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[明報] 香港律師會免費派口罩畀會員","createTime":"2020-02-26T02:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T02:58:35.000Z","uid":142878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2d3800353f4d38fef3f20fa3430893f16549ca5a","tid":1897812,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T02:47:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DFfUE4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDFfUE4G.jpg&h=f653ac04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n受武漢肺炎疫情影響下，巿面「一罩難求」，香港律師會今日（25日）發通告畀會員，話律師會將派發2.5萬個外科口罩畀律師行（包括本地及外地），同埋非私人執業嘅律師會員。<br />\n<br />\n律師會主席彭韻僖（Melissa）仲話，明白係疫情下仍然有律師行需要每日營業，其間有會員仲要外出公幹，同埋要返公司工作。一罩難求之下，Melissa都好犀利，搵到2.5萬個外科口罩免費派畀會員，佢話向海外訂購外科口罩時一度有延誤，不過最後都順利送來香港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200225/s00001/1582624846235/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200225%2Fs00001%2F1582624846235%2F&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWK7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=ef9a3f49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200225%2Fs00001%2F1582624846235%2F&h=be6469ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200225/s00001/1582624846235/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小學 學能測驗 - 數學<br />\n圖入面都有幾多盒口罩呢?"},{"pid":"e44aa5f2faed44b695b879c78509082ff846a8b1","tid":1897812,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T02:58:35.000Z","msg":"戴口罩好似著衫咁，點解派呢？"}]}